        HackerRank is the globally recognised developer skills assessment platform — deep coding IDE, AI-assisted interviews, and a community of 26M+ developers. If you are an Indian IT company looking for structured, rubric-based hiring assessments with India-first pricing and local data residency, AssessIQ is built for that.
